{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/5d/0d/23051_crt_73L8l.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5d/0d/23051_crt_73L8l.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/5d/0d/23051_crt_73L8l.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/5d/0d/23051_crt_73L8l.jpg"},"name":"ザク","summary":"拳王的近侧之人，在拳王受伤而隐匿的时候依然忠心耿耿地跟随在拳王身边，是类似于副官的存在。","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/f0/4a/16164_prsn_m5E0k.jpg?r=1718790157","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f0/4a/16164_prsn_m5E0k.jpg?r=1718790157","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/f0/4a/16164_prsn_m5E0k.jpg?r=1718790157","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/f0/4a/16164_prsn_m5E0k.jpg?r=1718790157"},"name":"拝真之介","short_summary":"拝 真之介（おがみ しんのすけ、1986年10月24日 - ）は、日本の男性声優。埼玉県出身。AIR AGENCY所属。クリスチャンである。","career":["seiyu"],"id":16164,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":23051},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/91/df/192705_crt_y9Yqn.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/91/df/192705_crt_y9Yqn.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/91/df/192705_crt_y9Yqn.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/91/df/192705_crt_y9Yqn.jpg"},"name":"ノブ","summary":"主人公。就職難の世紀末に、やっと見つけた就職先が拳王軍だった、かわいそうな一般人。\r\n意外と肝が据わっている。","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/d0/62/4262_prsn_tbC5r.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d0/62/4262_prsn_tbC5r.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/d0/62/4262_prsn_tbC5r.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/d0/62/4262_prsn_tbC5r.jpg"},"name":"下野紘","short_summary":"下野 紘は、日本の男性声優。アイムエンタープライズ所属。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":4262,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":192705},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/47/5c/192706_crt_2VOtm.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/47/5c/192706_crt_2VOtm.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/47/5c/192706_crt_2VOtm.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/4